data.description: Welcome to this charming split-level home located in the highly sought-after Big Bethel Heights neighborhood of North Hampton. This property boasts a lovely screened-in sunroom and a big backyard. Upon entering, you will be delighted by the space, light, and bright interior with beautiful hardwood flooring. The eat-in kitchen is perfect for preparing your favorite meals. With three generously sized bedrooms and one fully remodeled bathroom, there is ample space for everyone! You will love spending time outdoors, relaxing and unwinding with your loved ones on your screened-in porch, overlooking your level, fenced-in yard that provides privacy and shade. This unparalleled location offers a great balance of tranquility and convenience. Come and see it today!
